  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted Polish girl, they have, maybe on the side, their own acquaintances, but we were colleagues.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Breakfast, we made-- we had a little alcohol, little burner with a [INAUDIBLE] but we eat nothing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we ate outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't cook in the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably the-- the laundry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not to wash yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no bathroom at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the toilet, this is-- the Latin Quarter is old-- was in the lobby, and everything, it was a walk-up, and going up the stairs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is old [LAUGHS] stuff, you know, I don't think of it ever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how we survived this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody was the same things, not only I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For vacation, for the summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, yeah, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot to say, oh, that I forgot altogether now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to France with my brother, an older brother, who went to study also, and-- and he-- oh, I forgot, I mixed up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went first to Nancy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was admitted to the faculty of Nancy, and he was there to study agriculture, and I, medicine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But being there, I found out that north in Normandy, in a town, Rouen, they give credit for these who studied abroad.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was one year in Krakow, so I changed everything, and I went to Rouen with the idea that maybe they will give me credit for the year I was in Krakow, but it didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did the first year medicine, which is really only preparation to medicine, the entrance, the [NON-ENGLISH] science natural.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So over there, I did that in Rouen, and when I finished Rouen, I went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was your brother Michael?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
